{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"24776-walking-together","title":"Walking Together","description":"A walk to the clinic doesn’t have to be dull, when there are so many wonderful things to see on the way.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jade  Mathieson"],"illustrators":["Bianca de Jong"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/24776-walking-together"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527494/size3/453ffaa2b9d2495f11514f6313b85842.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527494/size6/453ffaa2b9d2495f11514f6313b85842.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85900/size6/fcf0e21ccde28d4bce62481a1e1e1fb3.jpg","text":"When we go walking and the road is long, we’ll walk together singing a song.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85901/size6/52803f696785d3c8a1ee44ff231b803c.jpg","text":"I am with you and you are with me. A journey is fun with our family.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85902/size6/aa69c4b9df8dd83f6d19cce4703dff10.jpg","text":"I’ll keep you cosy like a mother hen. She keeps her chicks warm under her wing.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85903/size6/3001fd19b554459fa49a87ea03a23c31.jpg","text":"If the rain starts to fall down from the sky, like that good hat I’ll keep your face dry.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85918/size6/fb7117b4211672b0cfb9bf8a03cad246.jpg","text":"If storm clouds get angry and grumble and moan, be brave, why cry? \nYou’re not alone.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85905/size6/a00e9406b6b1c698ac9e80ca41c64bd8.jpg","text":"We’re walking together so we never get bored. Look up! Look around! \nSee where we’ve explored!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85906/size6/820af865699760793ce646496804782e.jpg","text":"If you see something that’s funny to see, I don’t want to miss it. \nPlease share it with me!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85907/size6/1cee7746fad7e3ac8dcc124d2f274aab.jpg","text":"If your feet start to hurt from the distance we’ve passed, don’t worry, we’ve made it! Here’s the clinic at last.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85919/size6/574645eca9c854f209a5dd9324da63e5.jpg","text":"We all need to check our throat, lungs and ears. Get strong as you grow, it’s no reason for tears.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85909/size6/17bd59e1edbf41e7bab1419d3c174a8c.jpg","text":"Do you think it’s scary? Here, hold my hand. \nShe’ll check your blood pressure with this clever armband.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85910/size6/205473f4cff92386a80a34f19a08b2d5.jpg","text":"They give us our medicine, tell us what we should know, to keep us all healthy. \nNow back home we go.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85911/size6/8cbda13461eb40b58a1e6c2d364ffe07.jpg","text":"It’s okay to be tired, there’s so much we’ve seen. Now it’s your bedtime. \nSleep well and sweet dreams.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85912/size6/a86580c0caf828aa856f394764ca37d7.jpg","text":"14/15","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85913/size6/3ee5b8245988b85dd673321ba710132d.jpg","text":"15/15","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":218}}